{"tid":51442,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"（重開！）[人生無常從來唔係幾信］妹妹再見啦","createTime":"2016-12-23T08:30:28.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-29T03:48:09.000Z","uid":26635,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"643f4f8d0e50e058232319d2746e15b98f373726","tid":51442,"uid":26635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T08:30:28.000Z","msg":"頭先開左係感情台<br />\n<br />\n妹妹係我樓下一隻流浪貓<br />\n一年前突然出現係我樓下<br />\n好乖吓架<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/42.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又痴人 一叫佢就自己用個頭撞落你度叫摸摸<br />\n平時一見到佢都會狗衝上樓拿d貓糧佢食<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/23/135454_1fcdfbb5cc2adc879bd8f6c58b553c35.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F23%2F135454_1fcdfbb5cc2adc879bd8f6c58b553c35.jpg&h=463e3181&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/23/135742_092d0be3bad532af857ab9e953ad7aaa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F23%2F135742_092d0be3bad532af857ab9e953ad7aaa.jpg&h=c51ecf5e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我本身自己有養貓<br />\n如果養多隻實在太大負擔了<br />\n所以冇捕捉佢<br />\n就由佢係樓下自由自在<br />\n肚餓啊就黎我樓下 我就俾野佢食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n雖然有時佢會同其他貓狗打交<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又或者淋雨濕曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但一直都平安無事 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n今日下午當我食完晏番到門口<br />\n見到佢一隻貓柒下柒下咁望住灘水<br />\n我就諗住俾d驚喜佢 上樓拿包濕糧佢過下癮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n開曬係地下 請帖都派埋咁濟 都無動於衷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我女朋友話見到佢第三眼瞼出埋 <br />\n果刻我就知道仆街鳥<br />\n<br />\n即刻送佢去醫院<br />\n醫生話失溫 嚴重感染 脫水<br />\n已經病危<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/08j8RQe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F08j8RQe.jpg&h=b31d4d81&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/23/143350_d2d336163e91a53c180c539a30d48ea4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F23%2F143350_d2d336163e91a53c180c539a30d48ea4.jpg&h=dca95964&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/P4x7e0w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FP4x7e0w.jpg&h=2908c606&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一開始同妹妹接觸嘅時候 我就已經同自己講<br />\n佢係流浪貓 活著時間唔多 諗住盡可能俾到一兩餐溫飽佢 同佢玩下 開心過就算<br />\n到而家佢病危我都係好唔捨得佢 送左佢去留院<br />\n<br />\n今日好sad呀<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n希望各位巴絲可以珍惜眼前人（貓）"},{"pid":"85f620c7ee70ec15f422c12ac84970933401c37f","tid":51442,"uid":13432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T08:39:51.000Z","msg":"所以醫生係話有生命危險？"},{"pid":"0f5db75bc0de1261bba4472285b0869ce205f607","tid":51442,"uid":26635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T08:46:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>所以醫生係話有生命危險？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n醫生話佢嚴重失溫 白血球數量咁高<br />\n應該都要心理準備<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91c8c992f206b2771a2e950fb0b27cf4c491cff0","tid":51442,"uid":13432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T09:16:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>所以醫生係話有生命危險？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n醫生話佢嚴重失溫 白血球數量咁高<br />\n應該都要心理準備<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nTake care bro. 好好陪埋佢 <br />\n浪浪既生命就係咁化學"},{"pid":"4ef77eda048dc16498d0937b4394d204f47f8c6c","tid":51442,"uid":26635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T13:57:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/23/213919_c0da90eda830f2702c107ca7c0fea92a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F23%2F213919_c0da90eda830f2702c107ca7c0fea92a.jpg&h=0ce72cf7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bKVbDMi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbKVbDMi.jpg&h=ce9ff95b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n岩岩7點去左探妹妹<br />\n醫生話佢有尿毒症 加有d腸胃潰瘍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n應該係急性腎炎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n打左針 醫生話放係佢身邊冇咩作用<br />\n於是我就帶左佢番屋企<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9146Z05.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9146Z05.jpg&h=100b3ce8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n佢依家訓緊覺<br />\n<br />\n而家唯有每日帶佢打針 再睇佢做化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n加油妹妹"},{"pid":"894bde6acc0b689d7bac59fee4bcc07a25af41e5","tid":51442,"uid":16772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T14:32:51.000Z","msg":"巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  貓貓加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1eb718983da14b2d2731b5a20e0312bf051929eb","tid":51442,"uid":5052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T14:56:36.000Z","msg":"加油阿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 阿喵"},{"pid":"5563a9d4e244170fa728ce5bbac78af38e8720a6","tid":51442,"uid":26635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T16:27:29.000Z","msg":"捷報！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n係吊完鹽水同打完針之後 <br />\n佢返到屋企後 好似好d<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/67GxFxD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F67GxFxD.jpg&h=09b26759&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5V4F7j2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5V4F7j2.jpg&h=7efc6e01&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6cLmqGj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6cLmqGj.jpg&h=f9e9101f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/24/002232_2ea6ceb41eff2b7d4d2c99b2378a9202.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F24%2F002232_2ea6ceb41eff2b7d4d2c99b2378a9202.jpg&h=acb64630&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n而家會出個籠行下 岩岩飲左一啖水 仲屙左一大篤尿<br />\n醫生話會屙尿排毒係好轉嘅開始<br />\n依家有d開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n 但都係好驚佢夜晚去左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1db054ab78fdf9e344847d3b9f57a6e563ea0ef4","tid":51442,"uid":9155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T16:52:42.000Z","msg":"加油啊！"},{"pid":"016e430c0f67a8b78484e16199d2c1346830c755","tid":51442,"uid":24139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T17:04:04.000Z","msg":"希望每隻小動物都健康<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3783396d9c29a7bd325bdcd7b3d26fae40df77e6","tid":51442,"uid":31540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T19:17:22.000Z","msg":"加油呀貓貓<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04a2227f78a2c2ec4e98e5bf28eeabd727c00525","tid":51442,"uid":31626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T19:24:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile_big.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77cf06e3b4bba3a6281816dabc8bd5830ab50598","tid":51442,"uid":36942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T19:40:42.000Z","msg":"佢今日點呀？多謝你照顧佢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e5e32d78d3d51192037b4cbd4bbf23a0fd7c62e","tid":51442,"uid":26635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T20:27:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佢今日點呀？多謝你照顧佢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢岩岩狂叫叫醒我<br />\n好驚佢嘈到人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又屙左一篤尿 <br />\n不過屙左係廁所條毛巾 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有d驚佢同屋企本身隻野唔夾<br />\n仲未向病人釋懷善意<br />\n<br />\n佢好有中氣 應該唔會有咩問題掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cebd5661558515b6d20c0f361ae4485bfec2049f","tid":51442,"uid":26635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T03:40:09.000Z","msg":"有小小好轉啦<br />\n<br />\n雖然體溫依舊37度 都係不吃不喝<br />\n但精神狀態好左好多<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/24/113448_6eb5c915d1125f5746206c22ef492e64.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F24%2F113448_6eb5c915d1125f5746206c22ef492e64.jpg&h=d21583fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/o012ip7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fo012ip7.jpg&h=255d5c95&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/24/113441_76b7d3c7e44d3da543651bc0729882af.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F24%2F113441_76b7d3c7e44d3da543651bc0729882af.jpg&h=0ed5d638&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/v56h509.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fv56h509.jpg&h=762f3776&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今日開始曳曳啦<br />\n打個吊針都四圍走 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e1987124f9caac647966fdb7d8eaa71a841ab58","tid":51442,"uid":6408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T09:44:35.000Z","msg":"喵喵要快d好番<br />\n祝樓主同喵2017平安<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53a0dcd68c038599761580c5a5028c8d89aa4798","tid":51442,"uid":39177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T03:27:15.000Z","msg":"聽朝又八點九"},{"pid":"7cce63e748654f7007b5326ab1b93d8a3af24316","tid":51442,"uid":26635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T07:15:12.000Z","msg":"狀態更新<br />\n<br />\n醫生話本身佢就係老貓<br />\n加上有腎病<br />\n依家我地只能做嘅係支持療法<br />\n幫佢補充水分 同打抗生素<br />\n之後教我地點樣係屋企吊鹽水<br />\n因為醫生星期日休息 無法看診<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7xzUOa7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7xzUOa7.jpg&h=17677e18&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/655F209.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F655F209.jpg&h=763eaddf&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/25/150545_c04d38e0ee3afcd029bdb64abb633329.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F25%2F150545_c04d38e0ee3afcd029bdb64abb633329.jpg&h=8dc7b417&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BWM217E.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBWM217E.jpg&h=f3467afa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n琴晚係屋企吊鹽水<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n岩岩發現佢嘴邊有疑似乾燥嘅血塊<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n應該就<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb90d506b03c8e1fe79c59814e36d935fb362318","tid":51442,"uid":26635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T07:18:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n屋企隻原居民見到人地病仲惡人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/M6xxY4S.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FM6xxY4S.jpg&h=8fb38d45&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"309ec051349d0f3d84ea6e5417a872c51b438a8a","tid":51442,"uid":49359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T08:52:12.000Z","msg":"樓下有4母女<br />\n我成日好似痴漢跟尾<br />\n絡於同個阿媽同其中一個女好熟<br />\n平時餵開貓個阿婆見個阿媽會過我身邊俾我模都好驚訝<br />\n我都諗過如果都時佢地真係病<br />\n我會唔會帶佢地睇醫生<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個阿媽成日係我面前訓係地露出白色肚皮<br />\n但一模就拍我<br />\n只可以佢企係到時模佢<br />\n但個女露出肚皮就真係任模<br />\n其實係唔係有D貓就算露出肚皮都唔可以亂模"},{"pid":"f2614d79c66d5e8d128abc1c1e8d07cf32903f14","tid":51442,"uid":26635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T10:51:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓下有4母女<br />\n我成日好似痴漢跟尾<br />\n絡於同個阿媽同其中一個女好熟<br />\n平時餵開貓個阿婆見個阿媽會過我身邊俾我模都好驚訝<br />\n我都諗過如果都時佢地真係病<br />\n我會唔會帶佢地睇醫生<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個阿媽成日係我面前訓係地露出白色肚皮<br />\n但一模就拍我<br />\n只可以佢企係到時模佢<br />\n但個女露出肚皮就真係任模<br />\n其實係唔係有D貓就算露出肚皮都唔可以亂模</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n冇呀忍唔住冇計 又破財<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n流浪貓可以咁樣任摸ge都係真係少數<br />\n暫時都係見過2隻<br />\n一隻係妹妹 一隻係去泰國旅行果時遇到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{